{"tid":1933090,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲新西蘭3．20起禁外國人入境","createTime":"2020-03-19T05:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T06:08:27.000Z","uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5a9a47e286b6fb1dbf92762c8c05c83098e65edb","tid":1933090,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T05:57:25.000Z","msg":"因應新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情，澳洲總理莫里森周四（19日）宣布，當地時間周五（20日）晚上9時後，禁止非居民及非公民入境澳洲。<br />\n<br />\n新西蘭亦宣布，明日凌晨零時起禁止非居民及非公民入境新西蘭。<br />\n<br />\n截至本港時間今早（19日）11時，澳洲累計逾700宗確診，新西蘭累計28宗病例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200319/s00005/1584596356506/%e6%be%b3%e6%b4%b2%e6%96%b0%e8%a5%bf%e8%98%ad3-20%e8%b5%b7%e7%a6%81%e5%a4%96%e5%9c%8b%e4%ba%ba%e5%85%a5%e5%a2%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200319%2Fs00005%2F1584596356506%2F%25e6%25be%25b3%25e6%25b4%25b2%25e6%2596%25b0%25e8%25a5%25bf%25e8%2598%25ad3-20%25e8%25b5%25b7%25e7%25a6%2581%25e5%25a4%2596%25e5%259c%258b%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%2585%25a5%25e5%25a2%2583&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFXyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=d44fbc42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200319%2Fs00005%2F1584596356506%2F%25e6%25be%25b3%25e6%25b4%25b2%25e6%2596%25b0%25e8%25a5%25bf%25e8%2598%25ad3-20%25e8%25b5%25b7%25e7%25a6%2581%25e5%25a4%2596%25e5%259c%258b%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%2585%25a5%25e5%25a2%2583&h=b3df862d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200319/s00005/1584596356506/%e6%be%b3%e6%b4%b2%e6%96%b0%e8%a5%bf%e8%98%ad3-20%e8%b5%b7%e7%a6%81%e5%a4%96%e5%9c%8b%e4%ba%ba%e5%85%a5%e5%a2%83</a>"},{"pid":"88739242b2e18a9b799bc53d4537e5ef8acedde2","tid":1933090,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T06:08:27.000Z","msg":"因應<span style=\"color: red;\">武漢病毒</span>疫情，澳洲總理莫里森周四（19日）宣布，當地時間周五（20日）晚上9時後，禁止非居民及非公民入